Titolo: Major League Baseball 2K6

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Major League Baseball 2K6 (MLB 2K6) is a 2006 Major League Baseball licensed baseball video game developed by Kush Games and published by 2K Sports. It was released for Xbox 360, Xbox, GameCube, PlayStation 2 and PlayStation Portable.
It has new features, such as Inside Edge, World Baseball Classic, online experience and many more. This game also features various aspects that are new to baseball games, including fans shouting, the "swing stick", showboat catches, fans catching balls, and power rankings.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: 68
